title: Omega Vibes - Diaspora (1999) (Greek Music)@flac
description:
Diaspora features the Greek collective Omega Vibes, which is masterminded by Dimitris Panopoulos. 
The Greek artist centers his music on vocalists such as Glykeria and Christos Dantis, yet also emphasizes moody electronica soundscapes for the backdrop of his songs. In addition to the swirling ambience, Panopoulos also brings in quite a few musicians to add to the music, most notably guitarist Antonis Gounaris, violinist Nikos Hatzopoulos, and clarinetist Giorgos Kotsinis. (AMG)
